Interface F8<A,B,C,D,E,F$,G,H,I>

public interface F8<A,B,C,D,E,F$,G,H,I>

A transformation function of arity-8 from A, B, C, D, E, F$, G and H to I. This type can be represented using the Java 7 closure syntax.
